{
  "texts": [
    "While RATIONAL fine-tuned models still have lower compliance rates than base models as in Ap-✅Add Benign Rationale improved helpfulness without compromising robustness.",
    "❌Training only on Adversarial Rationale pendix C.3, It is important to note that our training dataset was not explicitly curated to optimize helpfulness.",
    "Yet, even with minimal intervention, adding 250 benign rationales from XSTEST, our model demonstrated a clear improvement in handling benign queries without significantly compromising safety.",
    "This suggests that further improvements in compliance could be achieved with targeted dataset curation.",
    "To further analyze the effect of the number of benign prompts on robustness and helpfulness, we conducted additional experiments in Appendix C.4."
  ]
}